      "description": "The CFD hemolysis model, calibrated against published FDA pump benchmark data, correctly ranks the five flow-speed operating points by relative hemolysis index (RH) and identifies the worst-case condition with sufficient fidelity to support the regulatory tolerance decision. The model prediction of RH < 1 relative to the predicate device is asserted to hold across the full COU envelope.",
